title: Jason Derulo Interview + More
itunes:title: Jason Derulo Interview + More
description:
Tuesday 3/21- Today on the show Jason Derulo came to visit and discussed his new investments, his issues with American Airlines and more. Also, Charlamagne gave Donkey of the Day to a teenager who jumped into a croc infested river to impress a girl, so we opened the phone lines to hear stories of the craziest thing they have done to impress someone.
